longBusinessSummary: aifinyo AG provides various financial solutions in Germany. It offers finance for the purchase of goods; contract financing services; work equipment leasing services; factoring services for entrepreneurs and freelancers; debt collection services; support services for the company's growth; and API-integration services. The company was formerly known as Elbe Finanzgruppe AG and changed its name to aifinyo AG in July 2019. aifinyo AG was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Dresden, Germany.
